<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> get the hots for someone • give it hot to someone</xh5><p> <i>get the hots for someone</i>—(sl.) be strongly attracted to a person sexually: Just as I suspected, Angie. You’re starting to <u>get the hots for</u> James.</p><p> <i>give it hot to someone</i>—(rare coll.) punish or scold smb. severely: I have <u>given it hot</u> to Grant Allen who did ... much the same as Romanes is doing now though not so barefacedly.</p><p> <i>See also: make it hot for someone / make someone hot.</i></p> </entry>
